	bool
	depends on DEFAULT_ENVIRONMENT_GENERIC_NEW
	depends on USB_GADGET_DFU
	default y
	help
	  Extend the defaultenv template with the 'dfu' boot entry, which
	  allows uploading the kernel and oftree over USB via the dfu protocol.

